ISSUE.TITLE: JobQuery no longer has method noRetriesLeft
ISSUE.DESCRIPTION: For some reason the `JobQuery` is missing the `noRetriesLeft` method. However it's implementation `JobQueryImpl` has it see [JobQueryImpl#L176](https://github.com/flowable/flowable-engine/blob/master/modules/flowable-job-service/src/main/java/org/flowable/job/service/impl/JobQueryImpl.java#L176). A Bonus suggestion from me, all methods that implement a method from an interface should have the `@Override` annotation, which will lead to compile problems and things like this would be avoided
